Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order to ride Whitebeard's ship,\NOden pushed himself to his limits,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he was swallowed up by the sea\Nat the last minute,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and drifted ashore on an unknown island\Nwhere he met a woman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Toki's and my child!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The word stands for peerless...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is Kozuki Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A samurai from a closed country...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I'll get to see him one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Crossing Swords!\NRoger and Whitebeard!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sukiyaki-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shogun, Sukiyaki-sama, is in critical condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sukiyaki-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the Land of Wano,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a serious matter occurred\Nwhich brought the Daimyo of each region to the Flower Capital.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I want Oden to succeed me as Shogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Sukiyaki-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But since Oden is not here now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a proxy until Oden returns,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in case anything happens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be this man\Nwho Oden cared for as if he was his little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Kurozumi Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oden cared for as if he was his little brother?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for giving me this opportunity\Nto clear Kurozumi's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never be able to look Sukiyaki-sama\Nand Oden-sama in the eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,To compensate for my grandfather's foolish act\Nand for other things,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I will assist\NOden-sama's enthronement to the best of my ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I will temporarily become\Na puppet until Oden-sama's return,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so I must ask for everyone's support!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is Sukiyaki-sama's decision,\Nthere is no way we can disobey it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Kurozumi....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I am sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:35.77,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,KUROZUMI OROCHI'S PAST
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurozumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurozumi! Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fast when running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there he is! Kurozumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,--Catch him!\N--Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Kurozumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kurozumi Clan needs to be exterminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kurozumi Clan is the vermin of the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's still around here.\NWe must find him and kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurozumi! You people are all criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make you pay for your crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to go through this\Nbecause of what that old geezer of mine did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:07:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to be hated\Njust for being a Kurozumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You scared me! W-What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it! I can see the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...become the Shogun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me, granny!\NWho the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what happened to your grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the details,\Nbut I heard he committed seppuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No! He was killed by Kozuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!\NBut I heard he committed some kind of crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Engaging in a power struggle\Nisn't a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A power struggle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take the reins,\Nyou can make the laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can legitimize any crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The previous Shogun from the Kozuki Clan\Ncouldn't have children!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No heirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Five clans that served under the Kozuki Clan\Nbecame unsettled...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,SHIMOTSUKI CLAN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is going to be the next Shogun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,KUROZUMI CLAN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:57.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,UZUKI CLAN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:09:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,While everyone was proudly thinking, "I am,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:58.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,AMATSUKI CLAN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:00.01,On Top,,0,0,0,,FUGETSU CLAN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,your grandfather was making preparations!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He was preparing to kill those annoying Daimyos\None by one with poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He got rid of them one after another\Nmaking them all look like inside jobs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shogun stressed over\Nthe series of Daimyo deaths,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and eventually became ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan went well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was within reach of taking the reins...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He was born!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The heir, Kozuki Sukiyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yes!\N--We're overjoyed for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A curse on you, Sukiyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Power was almost within his reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:10:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kurozumi Clan couldn't take the reins\Nand on top of that, the plan was exposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your grandfather committed seppuku\Nand the clan was put to an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Their territory, castle, and power\Nwere all taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,People grew to despise the name, Kurozumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and the members of the clan\Nended up in the streets!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose fault is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who made your life so miserable?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's responsible for your poverty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose fault is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because he was born!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozuki Sukiyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If he wasn't born,\Nyou'd have become the Shogun one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shogun-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shogun-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,--Shogun-sama!\N--Shogun-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shogun-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What beauties!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have become the Shogun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how aggravating, how galling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're my...\Nthe Kurozumi Clan's blood relative?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was out of the country all this time.\NIt was tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that my face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the power of the Clone-Clone Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna do as I tell you,\NI'll give you special power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The power you need to become the Shogun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Save money and produce weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The craftsmen in the Land of Wano\Nhave great skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Use them as bait\Nto win the backing of someone important!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:14.39,On Top,,0,0,0,,HAKUMAI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My whole family has fallen ill,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so I must feed them all somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for you. You can work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,A MONTH LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasuie-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Orochi has disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think it's just a coincidence,\Nbut the money in the safe is gone, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The money is gone, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,KURI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I met you at Yasu-san's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:14:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Orochi! Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is my family's illness got worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and I need money...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe Yasuie-sama so much,\NI can't borrow money from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. I see. Count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,--Oden-sama?!\N--Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Lend me money!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Lend me money!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please lend me money!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can pay you back for sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We are not doing well financially, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he's gonna pay it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this enough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not even close to being enough\Nto produce a massive amount of weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a place that has more money...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The next target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:26.07,On Top,,0,0,0,,FLOWER CAPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:29.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,KOZUKI SUKIYAKI (ODEN'S FATHER)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden?! Why did you suddenly come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:30.78,On Top,,0,0,0,,SHOGUN OF THE LAND OF WANO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And without your retainers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to ask you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you let him stay here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He works hard and can prepare medicine.\NHe's like my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, take good care of Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Shogun Sukiyaki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've finally made it this far!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:16.37,On Top,,0,0,0,,YEARS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sukiyaki-sama! Stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,--Sukiyaki-sama!\N--Sukiyaki-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Support Orochi for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sukiyaki-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,--I-I'll go get a doctor!\N--We'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Is somebody there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sukiyaki-sama! Are you all right?!\NSukiyaki-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of everything, Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't be so weak, Sukiyaki-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna become the Shogun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not so long afterward,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the news of the Shogun Sukiyaki's death\Nspread across the Land of Wano.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day in the fourth year of Oden's journey...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The fish are going crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a premonition of a natural disaster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're heading away from that island,\NWhite-Kichi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe some kind of monster lives there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco, go check!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I don't wanna spoil the fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Hiyori!\NMomonosuke, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we check it out, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go ashore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those savage animals running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's got to be on this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna catch me,\Nbring Garp or Sengoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no fun fighting against you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Whitebeard's ship\Non the opposite side of the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like they noticed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We just finished fighting, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard, huh? It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The birds seem distressed...\NThey must've come ashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it! We're only able to fight each other\Nwhile we draw breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My end is nearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be the last time I see you,\NWhitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?! He runs so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he a samurai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A samurai?!\NThat one everyone's talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Oden! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I plunder their treasure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a totally different situation!\NThe Roger Pirates are dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not listening at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun Modoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's as strong as they say.\NShould we stop him already, Rayleigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Gaban, Rayleigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You just wanna fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I smell a beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Divine Departure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I can't let that slide!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't touching each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger's earnest desire!\NHis dream to get to the last island on the Grand Line!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.90,0:23:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The key is the forbidden cultural heritage\Nof the Ponegliffs and Kozuki Oden!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Led by fate, these mighty two team up\Nand set sail for the place where no one has gone before!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Roger's Wish! A New Journey!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.83,0:23:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.44,0:23:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:48.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,